1. Imam jake *zube* koji mogu da grickaju sve vrste hrane. (I have strong *teeth* that can bite through all kinds of food.)
2. Kada mi se dese *bolovi u zubima*, obično koristim pastu za zube protiv osjetljivosti. (When I have *toothaches*, I usually use toothpaste for sensitive teeth.)
3. Mama mi je rekla da ako ne perem *zube* redovno, mogu dobiti karijes. (My mom told me that if I don't brush my *teeth* regularly, I can get cavities.)
4. Čišćenje *zuba* koncem je važno za održavanje oralne higijene. (Flossing your *teeth* is important for maintaining oral hygiene.)
5. Zubi mi se tresu kad vidim pauku. (My *teeth* chatter when I see a spider.)
6. Doktor je rekao da mi treba izvaditi tri *zuba*. (The doctor said I need to have three *teeth* extracted.)
7. Vuk je pokazao svoje *oštre zube* kad je naišao na lisicu. (The wolf showed his *sharp teeth* when he encountered a fox.)
8. Tokom fudbalske utakmice, igrač mi je slomio *zub*. (During the soccer game, a player broke my *tooth*.)
9. Čuvajte se *zubnih infekcija* jer mogu uzrokovati velike probleme. (Be careful of *tooth infections* because they can cause big problems.)
10. Dečak je dobio novčić pod jastuk jer mu je *Zubna vila* posjetila tokom noći. (The boy got a coin under his pillow because the *Tooth Fairy* visited him during the night.)